data.description: Ideally situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in the prestigious Lost Creek Estates, this luxurious home is a true gem, offering an idyllic lifestyle with easy access to the interstate, Atlanta, and the renowned Trilith Studios. Located just 20 minutes from Hartsfield-Jackson Atlanta International Airport, this property is perfect for those who need to balance travel and tranquility. Situated in close proximity to Peachtree City, Fayetteville, Senoia, shopping, and fine dining, you'll find all your modern conveniences and entertainment needs are within easy reach. Its location also offers a unique advantage as it falls within Fayette County and the highly regarded Whitewater School district. This much sought-after neighborhood makes it an ideal choice for families seeking the best in education and community. Enjoy the peace, comfort, and privacy that this property offers. You'll also find that the expansive 5-acre lot adds to the overall sense of seclusion and provides more than ample space for outdoor activities, entertaining and creative landscaping ideas. This immaculate residence boasts a timeless and well-maintained design, with a total finished square footage of 6,453 square feet. It features 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, providing plenty of room for everyone to easily find a place to call their very own. The master suite on the main is breathtaking with natural light beaming through the french doors that lead to the outdoor deck. Featuring an oversized walk-in closet connected to the master bath provides ample space. The second and third bedrooms are found at the top of the elegant, winding staircase to the right and to the left of the spacious landing. Bedroom number four and five are located in the basement. Fifth bedroom makes for an excellent office for the professional working from home. The recent updates enhance its appeal, with a brand-new roof installed just weeks ago, new stain on the rear deck, windows replaced within the last year, and a fresh coat of interior and exterior paint that revitalizes the entire property. For the chef in the house, the enormous gourmet island kitchen with breakfast bar and nook, also includes custom designed and built cabinetry, gleaming granite counter tops, and upgraded stainless steel appliances. Cooktop is currently electric but has gas conversion kit installed. There's also a huge walk-in pantry, and an adjacent sitting area complete with its own flagstone fireplace. It's the ideal place for trying out all of your latest recipes!! And if dining al fresco is your thing, enjoy French Toast and freshly brewed cappuccinos outside on the expansive deck. What could be better than that? One of the many highlights of this luxury home is its finished basement, which opens up countless possibilities for recreation, relaxation, or a personalized space to suit your family's lifestyle. Additionally, you'll find abundant storage throughout the home, ensuring that everything has its place, which allows you to enjoy an organized and clutter-free living environment. In summary, this luxurious home is the epitome of style, comfort, grace, and convenience. It's the kind of home where a lifetime of memories were meant to be created, shared, and treasured for years to come...and it's a standout choice for those looking for a prestigious and private lifestyle. But hurry, as properties like this don't come on the market very often, schedule your private viewing with your favorite Realtor or give us a call to schedule.
